{"word":"G635 - ἀποπλανάω - apoplanáō - ap-op-lan-ah'-o - Err","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποπλανάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apoplanáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-op-lan-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Err</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நெருக்கு, அமிழ்"},{"paragraph":"to cause to go astray to lead away from the truth to error"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G4105 - πλανάω - planáō - plan-ah'-o/4105\">G4105</a>; to <i>lead astray</i> (figuratively); passively to <i>stray</i> (from truth): - err, seduce.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4105/4105\">G4105</a>, <a href=\"#/G4106/4106\">G4106</a>, <a href=\"#/G4107/4107\">G4107</a>, <a href=\"#/G4108/4108\">G4108</a>, <a href=\"#/G635/635\">G635</a>"}]}